{"tid":1824683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃子華套戲就係黃圈能否自給自足既考驗","createTime":"2020-01-14T15:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T12:44:43.000Z","uid":19945,"like":90,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6e95b14290924640a00d85232167bcacc3c0b571","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"利申先：打手死全家<br />\n<br />\n本身子華套戲我係諗住唔睇<br />\n由一開始我都有屌過佢唔表態<br />\n但當近幾日慢慢見到套戲既背景<br />\n我無論點都會入場睇<br />\n為既就係證明比香港班商家佬同自私撚睇<br />\n黃圈係可以發展成主流<br />\n長遠要令香港人可增取更大話事權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地可以接受藍轉偽黃<br />\n為既就係要令黃圈賺到錢<br />\n我唔需要理子華係咩取態<br />\n佢講套戲係比香港人睇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地就要證明香港人可以養得起一個行業</span></span></strong><br />\n當你屌班偽人商家佬為錢時<br />\n你就係要做出糧比佢個個<br />\n你唔需要佢支持你 只需要佢簡奶你鞋底就得<br />\n零售同食肆暫時成績的確係有目共睹<br />\n但實際上我地仲未陷動到香港既經濟支柱<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞話成本千幾萬 大約要4000萬左右先回到本<br />\n投票我地有200萬人（+未投到票既後生仔）<br />\n你只需要100萬人支持睇一次已經講緊6000萬up<br />\n你想香港拎返根基？<br />\n做出好戲比人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46efcb7e7233a640062a53aaa334ac5248a3ad3","tid":1824683,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903e41b11eee42b96ed86971686a340a03b2c37a","tid":1824683,"uid":296607,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">應該點貼文宣?</div></span></strong></span><br />\n成條天橋被清過無數次，洗過好多次<br />\n但呢一張紙屹立不倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXej6E3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXej6E3.jpg&h=a6021d23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618b0222989f530d816981d911baf5880a5b15a1","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"我地要黃圈賺到錢<br />\n你先可以要班自私撚低頭<br />\n理鳩佢真定假都好<br />\n我地要支持自由係可以價值過億<br />\n唔係停留係個日餐廳賣多左幾多碗麵"},{"pid":"ea167b10033978a8add8bf8fcf88aedae363a6fe","tid":1824683,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"禮拜五講座，手足們唔該幫推置頂<br />\n<br />\n【行動post】【吳敏兒和你組工會】1月17日（五）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9010ff7e92c050c01930fe1efc4d5db9ddf34866","tid":1824683,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3533ab586a6c19c9f920aa612ff2fc9b4d7846e","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"19/1 遊行<br />\n23/1 比錢睇戲做宣傳"},{"pid":"2a7a8841ba00def2a0f1c4b690d36e0189abdd4b","tid":1824683,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"新年3大任務：119大遊行，年廿八和手足團年，各區和你宵，幫手share 比親戚朋友一齊過黃色新年啦<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822470</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWntZ1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWntZ1h.jpg&h=80a94863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"552b6e462b54a8c635bd06b5331841dc865bfe66","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"深圳的考驗：究竟深圳宗師深圳華返深圳拍電影算唔算本土？"},{"pid":"bf933742bbacbcb3175fb8cc305a78e70569353a","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"552b6e462b54a8c635bd06b5331841dc865bfe66","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"深圳的考驗：究竟深圳宗師深圳華返深圳拍電影算唔算本土？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b64fe71c1b1b142cc4e7e2b28db3e31cb87fb8","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bf933742bbacbcb3175fb8cc305a78e70569353a","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"552b6e462b54a8c635bd06b5331841dc865bfe66","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"深圳的考驗：究竟深圳宗師深圳華返深圳拍電影算唔算本土？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"黃店起碼會喺店外貼文宣<br />\n但係深圳華七個月喺深圳瞓咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"0c6900d76df15c3ecda05a320249dc38f5b207d5","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"香港經濟比人滲透20幾年<br />\n依家發展黃圈要直接幾個月連根拔起<br />\n究竟某部份連登仔(或滲透狗)係有幾天真<br />\n用你地個思維黃圈一世只可以發展成多幾間龍門<br />\n永遠唔會有大商家行業支持"},{"pid":"dd38915332c6e404dbe7b2d573a83beefd9e8e08","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"我理鳩得佢係咪實際奶共<br />\n一套戲一個機會<br />\n就係比唔同行業一個訊息<br />\n支持香港人一樣賺到錢<br />\n你唔係諗住成個行業為你反共？"},{"pid":"4c366270f1df8e1793462531ab052eb0791c92b8","tid":1824683,"uid":5031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"投票可以接受lesser evil<br />\n點解睇戲唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講明唔比中共審查既戲<br />\n因為佢慳錢用大陸野就唔睇"},{"pid":"e9da38f5c44249d53091cc7699481e8a78f70e3e","tid":1824683,"uid":26666,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"呢一次係證明黃色經濟圈的實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e664d5aefa744a4dd1d3e40f2d2e356132728e9f","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9da38f5c44249d53091cc7699481e8a78f70e3e","tid":1824683,"uid":26666,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"呢一次係證明黃色經濟圈的實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"深圳香港經濟圈萬歲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兒登風向：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大灣區達哥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深圳華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">龍門萬歲</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v25fFtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv25fFtQ.jpg&h=b3ba1f46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1254c3b17296b79d6db1680daee7e0b41806028","tid":1824683,"uid":82746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxshhCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxshhCE.jpg&h=f2dca26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d44c75d8731d051c29cd9e590fe9bdf7cf3d9823","tid":1824683,"uid":111153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"呢套戲關黃圈乜事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6b2260cb8f14c36bebe2ebb6305246f69abd56","tid":1824683,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d44c75d8731d051c29cd9e590fe9bdf7cf3d9823","tid":1824683,"uid":111153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"呢套戲關黃圈乜事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔個龍門將黃圈畫到去深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860955e70acc85adb60cff1f5ffc02b888be26dd","tid":1824683,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依個topic講左好撚多次啦屌你<br />\n咪撚哂位啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"54e1994c50fb76c0ffa887a7509e72275a61b13a","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqsxHJf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqsxHJf.png&h=fc3e5a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條傻系應黎都浪費時間<br />\n請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"e323a017ca2abd7f4549b6dc2e536d80db4cd474","tid":1824683,"uid":25635,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"我地可以接受藍轉偽黃<br />\n為既就係要令黃圈賺到錢<br />\n我唔需要理子華係咩取態<br />\n佢講套戲係比香港人睇<br />\n我地就要證明香港人可以養得起一個行業<br />\n<br />\n咁諗其實好危險<br />\n藍轉偽黃，其實即係俾錢對方洗<br />\n文化/娛樂產品絕對有作者想表達/傳遞訊息，低手就擺到明咁講，高手就潛而默化講左都唔覺....其實係應該要好小心作家背後嘅取態<br />\n一套講到明比香港人睇嘅戲...但過去半年佢對香港人嘅定義係乜嘢....林鄭係咪香港人？新坐館係咪香港人？你係咪香港人？....我諗你唔會將自己同佢地畫係同一條線稱大家都係香港人掛....咁黃子華講嘅香港人，係點樣香港人....？<br />\n<br />\n咁我又唔會捉住一兩句否定成個概念...黃色經濟圈可唔可以應用係影視文化，的確都需要我地實實在在咁企出黎，撐本土電影，先可以成事....可惜佢唔係一套十年，唔係一份最想填嘅試卷....做出黎嘅成績表，永遠唔係我想要嘅成績"},{"pid":"dd114824c462e3120901727874a60ae2b93dc584","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d44c75d8731d051c29cd9e590fe9bdf7cf3d9823","tid":1824683,"uid":111153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"呢套戲關黃圈乜事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"直接影響可能唔明顯<br />\n但點解返校比人打壓<br />\n因為香港影視業係奶共<br />\n睇重大陸市場忽略香港人感受<br />\n你要改變生態就要做到成績比人考慮<br />\n未來愈來愈多合拍奶共片唔好問點解<br />\n因為純香港電影根本唔值得投資"},{"pid":"4b0cbe026d859ab21bd477db129594880461602a","tid":1824683,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"對內容有興趣<br />\n雖然佢未必拍得好睇，不過會睇"},{"pid":"3e94027f65929399195fc78c17d85ac77cc285c6","tid":1824683,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q